52
00:02:51,919 --> 00:02:53,000
(Do you understand?)

53
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:55,199
(Your Highness,)

54
00:02:55,919 --> 00:02:56,919
(it's not that I don't trust you.)

55
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,319
(It's just that I have no confidence
in myself.)

56
00:02:59,759 --> 00:03:01,120
(I dare not bet on it.)

57
00:03:20,479 --> 00:03:21,680
(Silly boy.)

58
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:24,159
(Whether in Northern Liang or here,)

59
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,680
(you're very important)

60
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,800
(to me.)

61
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,599
Jeez!

62
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:30,800
Ridiculous!

63
00:03:31,319 --> 00:03:32,639
You're being ridiculous!

64
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:34,840
I thought you've done me a great honor

65
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:36,680
