as soon as possible.

79
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:01,520
Dad,

80
00:04:02,479 --> 00:04:04,400
you need to think this through.

81
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:07,520
Now, Mrs. Bai has the final say.

82
00:04:08,199 --> 00:04:09,639
But in a few years,

83
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,400
it'll be Bai Yu has the final say.

84
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,919
If we fire his beloved woman

85
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:17,360
for no reason,

86
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:18,920
we'll get

87
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,000
