90
00:04:24,199 --> 00:04:25,600
But what are we going to tell

91
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,639
Mrs. Bai?

92
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:30,240
Well,

93
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:32,439
