men's clothing lately, haven't you?

94
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:32,959
Yes.

95
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:34,600
Why don't

96
00:04:34,998 --> 00:04:37,118
we leave this difficult task

97
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,040
to Long Mengli?

98
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,800
If she screws up,

99
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:41,680
we can ask her to resign

100
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,600
rightfully.

101
